data.description: Must see this charming home in Commerce City! This home features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms & a bonus non-conforming bedroom in the basement with its own bathroom! This home is a rare find with the OVERSIZED 3-car garage with 8 ft. doors, a ventilation hood & 220V! You could run your own business as the property is located in unincorporated Adams County. The garage heater & A/C are included. Very long driveway for additional parking or an RV. This home greets you with brand-new carpet and the original hardwood flooring is underneath. Fully finished basement with a separate laundry room area with additional storage. All appliances stay and there is NO HOA! Low yard maintenance as both the front & backyard are professionally Xeriscaped. Very cozy & fun backyard with a privacy fence, shed, dog run, adorable patio area, beautiful perennials that bloom from Spring until the fall and lots of yard art with solar! New sewer line with yard clean outs. Easy access to Denver & major highways. All you need to do is move in and make this your happy home!!
